{% set products = craft.entries().type('products').all() %}
<section class="hero">
  <h1>{{ entry.title }}</h1>
  <div class="intro">
    <p class="large">What is most important to you in finding the right motion tracking product? Do you need a wireless product? The highest level of precision tracking? Or something else? Scroll down to the Motion Tracking Selection Guide below to view your best options.</p>
